channel.title: [562]Developers[Rs2hd]
channel.description:
I am currently working on a project: and prefer working in team than alone, it'll motivate me more and the project would grow faster.
Here are the requirements to join the team: [ul][li]You must have general Java knowledge;[/li] [li]Preferably knowing a bit about rs2hd sources;[/li] [li]Be mature, respect me and I'll respect you;[/li] [li]Having at least few hours per week to work on the project.[/li][/ul]
That's all I'm requiring and I don't consider it much, so if you want to join me, post below or PM me, thanks!
